      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; commercial solver residual convergence monitoring is accepted as sufficient at Gradation 1.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, detailed numerical solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not required. Convergence to residuals below 1e-5 for all equations was confirmed for each simulation. This satisfies the Gradation 1 requirement without full solver error assessment."
    },
    {
