      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; nominal input values from published literature and device specifications satisfy Gradation 1.",
      "rationale": "Fluid properties (viscosity, density) and boundary conditions (flow rates, rotational speeds) were taken from published FDA benchmark documentation and device specifications. Nominal values were used without formal uncertainty propagation, which is acceptable at Gradation 1 for MRL 2."
